1221
01:16:11,406 --> 01:16:12,406
No.

1222
01:16:13,075 --> 01:16:14,702
It's not possible?

1223
01:16:14,703 --> 01:16:15,703
No.

1224
01:16:16,178 --> 01:16:19,739
