01:22:53,108 --> 01:22:56,407
Corporal Jeffrey Owen Barnes,
Marine Barracks Windward...

1324
01:22:56,478 --> 01:22:58,503
Guantanamo Bay, Cuba.

1325
01:22:58,580 --> 01:23:02,914
Corporal Barnes, name some reasons
why a Marine would receive a Code Red.

1326
01:23:02,984 --> 01:23:06,385
Being late for platoon
or company meetings.

1327
01:23:06,454 --> 01:23:10,356
Keeping his barracks in disorder.
Falling back on a run.

1328
01:23:10,425 --> 01:23:12,916
- Have you ever received a Code Red?
- Yes, sir.

1329
01:23:12,994 --> 01:23:16,555
We were doing seven-man assault drills,
and my weapon slipped.

1330
01:23:16,631 --> 01:23:19,930
It was 'cause it was over 100 degrees,
and my palms were sweaty...

1331
01:23:20,001 --> 01:23:23,664
and I'd forgotten to use the resin
like we were taught.

1332
01:23:23,738 --> 01:23:25,262
