1353
01:24:26,401 --> 01:24:29,199
'Cause Dawson
would kick my butt, sir.

1354
01:24:29,270 --> 01:24:33,206
Good enough. Captain Ross
is gonna ask you some questions now.

1355
01:24:34,576 --> 01:24:36,510
Corporal Barnes...

1356
01:24:37,979 --> 01:24:40,470
I hold here the Marine Outline
