1357
01:24:40,548 --> 01:24:42,311
- Are you familiar with this book?
- Yes, sir.

1358
01:24:42,383 --> 01:24:44,044
- Have you read it?
- Yes, sir.

1359
01:24:44,119 --> 01:24:47,418
Would you turn to the chapter
